    "Id": "vehiclechassisdef_MAXIM_C3S",
    "Name": "Maxim (C3S)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Maxim Heavy Hover Transport (C3S)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>8/12 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>165 ICE</color></b>\n\nThe Maxim is a hover APC designed to provide cover fire for deploying infantry and to support them in the field. To that end, the Maxim is heavily armored for an APC and is outfitted with a variety of weapons.\n\nThis version is used in conjunction with the Maxim C3 Master. Removing the machine guns and ammunition, it expands the infantry bay to four tons, allowing it to carry a squad of battle armor. It also carries a C3 Slave and keeps the TAG system.",
